author: @robertfraser9873
content: I worry that for the Brazil show that they will not be able to stage this performance during LTT. All the shows have been staged at indoor venues so that the lighting and prop rig can be secured to the venues roof. In an outdoor setting how will they manage that? Also any wind will blow the drop down screens to move about and the projections will be out of focus.
